JSON Import Format Reference
{
"namespace1": {
"key1": "value1",
"key2": "value2"
},
"namespace2": {
"nested": {
"key3": "value3"
}
}
}
This creates:

- namespace1::key1 = "value1"
- namespace1::key2 = "value2"
- namespace2.nested.key3 = "value3"
